drivel: drivel (GNOME Journal Editor)
drivel:
drivel: Drivel is a GNOME client for working with online journals, also known 
drivel: as weblogs or simply blogs. It retains a simple and elegant design 
drivel: while providing many powerful features, including support for LiveJournal, 
drivel: Blogger, MovableType, Advogato, and Atom journals (like WordPress and 
drivel: Drupal), offline composition and editing, and journal system extensions, 
drivel: including LiveJournal security groups and MovableType categories.
